439
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Gut.</font>

440
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:14,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Es sieht schön aus.</font>

441
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:17,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Duftet wunderbar und</font>
